  <deactivateThisPage>1</deactivateThisPage>
  <description><![CDATA[<p>The only 5 star hotel in <a data-udi="umb://document/870730cefeb2441dab9ccfec19c2fe88" href="/{localLink:umb://document/870730cefeb2441dab9ccfec19c2fe88}" title="Meribel">Méribel</a>, located in the very heart of the resort opened its doors for the first time in December 2012. The design provides the ultimate in luxury with refined and elegant furnishings throughout. Relax in the fabulous piano bar and dine in the gastronomic Michelin star restaurant serving excellent food. There is also the amazing 500m² Spa Nuxe with swimming pool, sauna and steam room as well as aqua biking, hydromassage jets, and water sprays. Make your way to the slopes via the private lift from the boot room and ski less than a minute to gain access to the Chaudanne lifts.</p>]]></description>
